Join the JunctionX Singapore Family

We are JunctionX Singapore, part of JunctionX â€“ a volunteer-lead community effort around the world. Our headquarters is located at Startup Sauna in Finland but the Junction team as a whole spreads out all around the globe. The thing that connects us all? A passion for empowering people to create with technology. Join us!
{/*
We organize hackathons, speaker events, coding workshops and other tech events around the year. We have something for every skill set and interest: take on new challenges, explore, and gain new experiences in Junction events!

A Diverse Team
{/*
*/}
Our volunteers are involved in all parts of the production, from partnership and website teams to marketing and branding. As a volunteer you get a unique opportunity to learn how to organize world-class events and a chance to join an awesome community of people from all over the world. What do we expect from you? Nothing but enthusiasm and eagerness to learn.

Junction events are organized throughout the year, including JunctionX hackathons around the world. The winning team for JunctionX Singapore will get the opportunity to go to the annual main event in Finland: next up, Junction 2020! If youâ€™re into tech at all, it is the place to be â€“ a full weekend of hacking with around other tech heads & hustlers in an awesome venue and atmosphere like no other. An experience you do not want to miss out on. Stay tuned for more information!
